perl-file-sharedir: perl-file-sharedir (Locate per-dist and per-module shared files)
perl-file-sharedir:
perl-file-sharedir: The intent of File::ShareDir is to provide a companion to
perl-file-sharedir: Class::Inspector and File::HomeDir, modules that take a process that
perl-file-sharedir: is well-known by advanced Perl developers but gets a little tricky,
perl-file-sharedir: and make it more available to the larger Perl community.
perl-file-sharedir:
perl-file-sharedir: http://search.cpan.org/dist/File-ShareDir/
